# LeakSanitizer suppressions for the test suite.
#
# These entries suppress leaks that originate entirely inside third-party code that
# the rendering tests pull in (GPU drivers, the Vulkan loader/ICDs, DXVK and the
# font libraries). Those libraries allocate caches/handles that are only released
# when the process is torn down, which LeakSanitizer reports at exit. They are not
# leaks in this repository and cannot be fixed here, so we ignore them by module.
#
# Matching is by substring against any frame's function name or module path. Keep
# these patterns specific to third-party modules so real leaks in our own code are
# still reported.

# Font stack (fontconfig pattern/cache, freetype)
leak:fontconfig
leak:libfreetype

# NVIDIA proprietary driver / CUDA
leak:libcuda
leak:libnvidia
leak:libGLX_nvidia

# Vulkan loader + ICDs (RADV / generic), validation layers
leak:libvulkan
leak:radeon
leak:libVkLayer

# Mesa / generic GL software stack
leak:libGL
leak:swrast
leak:libdrm

# DXVK (prebuilt D3D8->Vulkan translation layer) internal caches
leak:dxvk

# Leak some testdata
leak:SetupPipeTestCases